  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\n少々お時間をいただいてもいいでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ good work.\nMay I have a moment of your time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6666666627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. What's up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.7986164529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "先ほど、さとみさんからアイドルが出場する\nダンス大会の話を聞いたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just now‚ Satomi-san told me about\nidols participating in a dance competition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4333334882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そのことか。ちょうどみんなに知らせようと\n思ってたんだ。この番組なんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ about that. I was just about to let everyone know.\nIt's this program…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.0860994298,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2247.2339034999995,
          "startTime": 20.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "あ……この番組、知ってます\n人気アイドルが沢山出演する配信番組ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I know this program.\nIt's a streaming show where many popular idols come out‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0333330432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "生配信をすれば同時接続二万人超えが当たり前で\nアーカイブの再生回数も平均で数十万回……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's a live stream‚ exceeding 20‚000 viewers is normal thing‚\nand the average number of archive views is in the hundreds of thousands…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.6333330432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "私もよく、千紗や雫ちゃんと観ています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I often watch it with Chisa and Shizuku-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.5573891917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "知ってるなら話が早いな。今回はこの番組で\n特別にダンス大会が開かれることになってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you know about it‚ then it's straightforward. This time‚\nthere will be a special dance competition on this show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.0056915561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "とはいっても、普通のダンス大会じゃない。自分が\n所属するグループ以外の曲で踊らなきゃいけないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's not just any dance competition. Participants have to\ndance to songs from groups other than their own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0390259067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……決められた期間内に、他人の曲でどれだけ\nダンスを仕上げられるかを競うんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… So it's a competition to see how well you can prepare\ndances to other people's songs within a set period.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3000004728,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}